OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAdele says backlash to Las 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FVegas residency            
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpostponement was brutal    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Adele has said the "brutal" reaction to
OL,6, the postponement of her Las Vegas      
OL,7, residency earlier this year left her   
OL,8, feeling like "a shell of a person".    
OL,10,FIn January, the singer scrapped her    
OL,11,Fdates 24 hours before opening night,   
OL,12,Ftelling fans the show was not ready.   
OL,14,FSpeaking to BBC Radio 4's Desert Island
OL,15,FDiscs, Adele said postponing her       
OL,16,Fthree-month residency left her         
OL,17,F"devastated", but said she stood by the
OL,18,Fdecision.                              
OL,20,FOn Friday, she told fans the shows     
OL,21,Fwould be rearranged "very, very soon". 
